parameters:
Young female explorer Ect: Welcome, Clea-san! Did you enjoy
the ruins exploration?

Young female explorer Ect: Don't make such a scary face!
Shall I try to guess what Clea-san wants to know?

Young female explorer Ect: Clea-san, you want to know how I
found out that you killed your father, right?
Clea: Did you learn everything from the power of that gem?

Young female explorer Ect: Hmm, not quite. It was actually a
chubby old man named Psema who gave me the hint.

Young female explorer Ect: People who have finished their
business with the black request form from the Adventurer's
Guild are killed!
Mage Relm: That's not true! It's a misunderstanding--

Young female explorer Ect: So I investigated inside the
Adventurer's Guild! It was tightly secured, so I used the
power of the gem there.

Young female explorer Ect: What that appraiser said was a
little wrong. This gem only amplifies negative emotions and
gives me magical power!

Young female explorer Ect: Even the teleportation earlier
was thanks to the power of the gem! It's amazing, right? I
can do even more fun things with it!
Clea: Please tell me the purpose of calling me soon.

Young female explorer Ect: By the way, how did it feel when
you killed your father?

Young female explorer Ect: I want to know! Clea-san, what
were you thinking, what were you feeling, what were you
thinking?

Young female explorer Ect: Hehehe, I want to hear it
later... Just the two of us, ahaha, ahahahaha!

Clea: As someone who has lived as a avenger, I understand
what Ect is thinking.

Young female explorer Ect: Why, why, why, why! Why is my
beloved Clea-san pointing a sword at me?!

Young female explorer Ect: Well, whatever... Let's defeat
her and then carry out the plan.

Young female explorer Ect: Clea-san, I'll make sure you
don't die.
Young female explorer Ect: Please don't die, okay?

Clea: You know the three principles of the Adventurer's
Guild, right? Don't betray, don't lie, don't run away.

Clea: This time, it's not a request from Ect, but rather an
invitation. In other words, I consider it a problem that
occurred outside of the Adventurer's Guild.

Clea: So please choose. If you choose your life, then hand
over the jewel.

Clea: Thank you for choosing your life. Melos-san told me to
rely on you about Ect.
Clea: I'm glad we were able to avoid betraying Melos-san.
Young female explorer Ect: *sniffle*... What should I do?

Young female explorer Ect: I love Clea-san just as much as I
love Papa.

Clea: Please decide for yourself, that's what being an
adventurer is about.

Priestess Sophia: Because we don't belong to the
Adventurer's Guild, there's something we can talk about.

Priestess Sophia: I will tell you why Melos-san became like
that...
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Clea (Unbelievable strength... but her emotions are becoming
more and more unstable as a result of that strength...)

Young female explorer Ect: I'm so relieved! I was worried
that Clea-san might die!

Clea: It's not over yet. I can still wield my sword and
fight...
Young female explorer Ect: Take this!☆
Clea: What did you do to everyone... my comrades!?

Young female explorer Ect: I want to be alone with Clea-
san! That's why I asked her to leave the ruins.

Young female explorer Ect: You have such a worried
expression... It's really frustrating, but never mind!
Young female explorer Ect: Well then...
Would you like to skip the adult scene?
